{"tid":2006354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人懷疑自己有過武肺","createTime":"2020-05-07T17:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T17:13:05.000Z","uid":36775,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5190354a604656b81f50d929be849eb8b7f5acf4","tid":2006354,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T17:07:01.000Z","msg":"有無人有同我一樣經歷<br />\n我係一月尾至三月中一直乾咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最初有發燒，但食完必理痛退咗燒，但仲一直乾咳<br />\n最嚴重戈陣十幾秒就咳一次，大約keep住1-2個星期，其後大約一分鐘咳一次<br />\n所以咳咗幾日去睇醫生(大約一月尾)，醫生話無發燒所以唔會係武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢開咗啲感冒藥同止咳藥<br />\n但係食咗藥都照咳無好轉<br />\n係三月頭再自己去藥房執藥，但都無好轉<br />\n大約四月頭至中無啦啦好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係轉季問題定係武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲frd都話有過相同經歷"},{"pid":"42aaeb94a7e75e701d70be0aaa2241515466ef15","tid":2006354,"uid":27824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T17:13:05.000Z","msg":"十個香港人有九個都自我懷疑過"}]}